head.note:
This telegram was sent to the following countries:
                        Belgium, with instructions also to convey to Luxemburg Government; Bolivia;
                        Bulgaria; Chile; Colombia; Costa Rica; Cuba; Denmark; Dominican Republic;
                        Ecuador; Egypt, with instructions also to convey to Saudi Arabian
                        Government; El Salvador; Estonia; Greece; Guatemala; Haiti; Honduras;
                        Hungary; Iran, with instructions also to convey to Afghan Government; Iraq;
                        Ireland; Italy; Latvia; Liberia; Lithuania; Mexico; Netherlands; Nicaragua;
                        Norway; Panama; Paraguay; Peru; Portugal; Rumania; Spain; Sweden;
                        Switzerland; Thailand; Turkey; Uruguay; Venezuela; and Yugoslavia.
